high_descs: Take a few steps to the right, turn around, face the microwave
Take the salt shaker from in front of the microwave
Turn around, head to the counter, open the cabinet door
put the salt shaker inside the cabinet, close the cabinet door
turn around, head to the microwave
Take the salt shaker from in front of the microwave
Turn around, head to the counter, open the cabinet door
put the salt shaker inside the cabinet, close the cabinet door

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the microwave.
Pick up the closest pepper grinder off of the counter.
Turn left and walk to the wall, then turn left and walk over to the counter.
Open the rightmost lower cabinet door below the counter and put the pepper grinder inside to the left of the pepper grinder that's already in there.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the microwave.
Pick up the pepper grind off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Open the rightmost lower cabinet door below the counter and put the pepper grinder inside to the left of the pepper grinders that are already in there.
anns.task_desc: Move two pepper grinders into a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the counter
Pick up the salt on the counter
Turn around, go forward
Put the salt in the cupboard
Turn around, go forward to the counter
Pick up the salt
Turn around, go forward
Put the salt in the cupboard
